# Auto-generated artifacts in the analyzer subtree.
# Mirrors upstream `JackRobards/lit-analyzer`'s `.gitignore` patterns, scoped
# to our `packages/analyzer/*` layout. `tsc --build` writes:
#   - `lit-analyzer/`: rootDir=./src, outDir=./   (so `lib/`, `test/`, `scripts/`
#                                                  and `index.*` mirror `src/**`
#                                                  at the package root)
#   - `ts-lit-plugin/`: outDir=./lib              (note: `index.js` here is the
#                                                  hand-written CJS bridge —
#                                                  do NOT ignore)
#   - `vscode-extension/`: outDir=out, plus `built/` from esbuild + copy-to-built
/packages/analyzer/lit-analyzer/lib/
/packages/analyzer/lit-analyzer/test/
/packages/analyzer/lit-analyzer/scripts/
/packages/analyzer/lit-analyzer/index.js
/packages/analyzer/lit-analyzer/index.js.map
/packages/analyzer/lit-analyzer/index.d.ts
/packages/analyzer/lit-analyzer/index.d.ts.map

/packages/analyzer/ts-lit-plugin/lib/

/packages/analyzer/vscode-extension/out/
/packages/analyzer/vscode-extension/built/

# Library summary emitted by `@genexus/kasstor-build` alongside the TS artifact.
**/library-summary.json

*~
